results.name: Number of, not necessarily connected, regular simple graphs on n vertices with girth at least 5.
link: Jason Kimberley, Index of sequences counting not necessarily connected k-regular simple graphs with girth at least g
xref: Not necessarily connected k-regular simple graphs with girth at least 5: this sequence (any k), A185305 (triangle); specified degree k: A185325 (k=2), A185335 (k=3).
Not necessarily connected regular simple graphs with girth at least g: A005176 (g=3), A185314 (g=4), this sequence (g=5), A185316 (g=6), A185317 (g=7), A185318 (g=8), A185319 (g=9).
